{"title":"2025 Sea Otter Classic Prelude: PNW Marin Giveaway Bike, Hudski Dualist Hardtail, Mondraker Grinduro Edition, Slug Ti Gravel Bike, Sage Dropimator, and Small Monsters Mosaic – John Watson","link":"https://theradavist.com/2025-sea-otter-marin-hudski-mondraker-slug-sage-mosaic/","date":1744282829000,"content":"<p><em>John and Spencer are walking the dusty aisles of Laguna Seca for the 2025 <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/tag/sea-otter-classic/\" target=\"_blank\">Sea Otter Classic</a>. To kick off our coverage this year, we’ve got a prelude with a few choice bikes to showcase before the show officially opens tomorrow…</em><span></span></p>\n<p><strong>The Radavist thanks <a href=\"https://1up-usa.com/\" target=\"_blank\">1-Up USA</a> for sponsoring our Sea Otter Classic coverage and our independent Reportage!</strong></p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-PNW-Components-Marin-Bikes-Giveaway-1.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-PNW-Components-Marin-Bikes-Giveaway-1.jpg?w=650&amp;quality=75 640w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-PNW-Components-Marin-Bikes-Giveaway-1.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-PNW-Components-Marin-Bikes-Giveaway-1.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-PNW-Components-Marin-Bikes-Giveaway-4.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-PNW-Components-Marin-Bikes-Giveaway-4.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-PNW-Components-Marin-Bikes-Giveaway-4.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-PNW-Components-Marin-Bikes-Giveaway-4.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-PNW-Components-Marin-Bikes-Giveaway-6.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-PNW-Components-Marin-Bikes-Giveaway-6.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-PNW-Components-Marin-Bikes-Giveaway-6.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-PNW-Components-Marin-Bikes-Giveaway-6.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-PNW-Components-Marin-Bikes-Giveaway-15.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-PNW-Components-Marin-Bikes-Giveaway-15.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-PNW-Components-Marin-Bikes-Giveaway-15.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-PNW-Components-Marin-Bikes-Giveaway-15.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.signupanywhere.com/signup/efcrqqzq\" target=\"_blank\">PNW Components and Marin Bikes Alpine Trail XR Giveaway</a></h3>\n<p>We’re stoked to help out <a href=\"https://www.pnwcomponents.com/\" target=\"_blank\">PNW Components</a> and Marin Bikes give away a super silver customized <a href=\"https://www.marinbikes.com/bikes/2024-alpine-trail-xr\" target=\"_blank\">Marin Alpine Trail XR</a>, size large. You can win this very bike! Outfitted with PNW Components, <a href=\"https://groundkeepercustom.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Ground Keeper Custom</a>, <a href=\"https://trpcycling.com/collections/drivetrain\" target=\"_blank\">TRP groupset</a>, and custom silver <a href=\"https://reservewheels.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Reserve aluminum wheels</a>. Must be 18+ and a resident of the US to enter.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.signupanywhere.com/signup/efcrqqzq\" target=\"_blank\">Roll on over and enter to win</a>!</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-Hudski-Dualist-Hardtail-13.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-Hudski-Dualist-Hardtail-13.jpg?w=650&amp;quality=75 640w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-Hudski-Dualist-Hardtail-13.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-Hudski-Dualist-Hardtail-13.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-Hudski-Dualist-Hardtail-5.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-Hudski-Dualist-Hardtail-5.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-Hudski-Dualist-Hardtail-5.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-Hudski-Dualist-Hardtail-5.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-Hudski-Dualist-Hardtail-8.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-Hudski-Dualist-Hardtail-8.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-Hudski-Dualist-Hardtail-8.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-Hudski-Dualist-Hardtail-8.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-Hudski-Dualist-Hardtail-3.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-Hudski-Dualist-Hardtail-3.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-Hudski-Dualist-Hardtail-3.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-Hudski-Dualist-Hardtail-3.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://hudskibikes.com/products/dualist-all-terrain-bike\" target=\"_blank\">Hudski Bikes Dualist</a> 50 mm Travel <a href=\"https://ridefox.com/collections/fox-32-step-cast\" target=\"_blank\">Fox 32 Step Cast</a> Hardtail</h3>\n<p>John’s coming off a rad Shop Visit with Hudski Bikes, so expect a deeper look into the brand and the new boost-spaced Dualist platform. You might recall that we first debuted the <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/hudski-dualist-v3-updates/\" target=\"_blank\">Dualist at Sea Otter last year</a>. Brian from Hudski was inspired by <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/bike-hacks-how-i-made-my-custom-suspension-fork/\" target=\"_blank\">Travis Engel’s Bike Hack</a> tutorial, where he re-built his Fox 32 fork to 85 mm travel for his drop bar 29er. Fox sent Hudski a fork for the brand’s Sea Otter builds, and the final bike came together too sick in this “eggplant” paint color. Brian rebuilt this Fox 32 Step Cast from 100 mm to 50 mm. Unfortunately, the 32 steerer is too short to fit on the large or x-large frames but it looks great on this size medium.</p>\n<p>You can pre-order the <a href=\"https://hudskibikes.com/products/dualist-all-terrain-bike?variant=41527490215999\" target=\"_blank\">Dualist at Hudski</a>.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-Mondraker-Arid-Aluminum-Grinduro-Edition-29.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-Mondraker-Arid-Aluminum-Grinduro-Edition-29.jpg?w=650&amp;quality=75 640w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-Mondraker-Arid-Aluminum-Grinduro-Edition-29.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-Mondraker-Arid-Aluminum-Grinduro-Edition-29.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-Mondraker-Arid-Aluminum-Grinduro-Edition-16.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-Mondraker-Arid-Aluminum-Grinduro-Edition-16.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-Mondraker-Arid-Aluminum-Grinduro-Edition-16.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-Mondraker-Arid-Aluminum-Grinduro-Edition-16.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-Mondraker-Arid-Aluminum-Grinduro-Edition-27.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-Mondraker-Arid-Aluminum-Grinduro-Edition-27.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-Mondraker-Arid-Aluminum-Grinduro-Edition-27.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-Mondraker-Arid-Aluminum-Grinduro-Edition-27.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-Mondraker-Arid-Aluminum-Grinduro-Edition-35.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-Mondraker-Arid-Aluminum-Grinduro-Edition-35.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-Mondraker-Arid-Aluminum-Grinduro-Edition-35.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-Mondraker-Arid-Aluminum-Grinduro-Edition-35.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://app.viralsweep.com/sweeps/full/e423cf-203874?framed=1\" target=\"_blank\">Mondraker Arid Grinduro Edition</a></h3>\n<p>Spanish bike brand <a href=\"https://mondraker.com/us/en\" target=\"_blank\">Mondraker</a> displayed this one-of-a-kind Arid in honor of the 10-year Anniversary of <a href=\"https://grinduro.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Grinduro</a>. The brand is the host sponsor of the events in California and Scotland. The poppin’ purple paint is done in-house at its headquarters in Elche, Spain. Perhaps more blingy than the paint is this build kit. <a href=\"https://www.sram.com/en/sram/road/series/apex-d1\" target=\"_blank\">SRAM Apex AXS</a> with special support from <a href=\"https://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;merchant_id=1ee84457-7e2e-498d-87ed-ecb578e5c230&amp;website_id=6ec3743b-a948-4c16-9d12-4b79ac107f25&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fchrisking.com%2Fproducts%2Fchris-king-grd23\" target=\"_blank\">Chris King GRD23 wheels</a>, King seat clamp, <a href=\"https://www.paulcomp.com/shop/components/boxcars/boxcar-stem/\" target=\"_blank\">Paul Components Boxcar stem</a> and Tall &amp; Handsone post, and Schwalbe with some sweet 700 x 2.0″ G-One RX tires… and Mondraker is giving this one away!</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://app.viralsweep.com/sweeps/full/e423cf-203874?framed=1\" target=\"_blank\">Sign up to win this Arid</a>.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-Slug-Bikes-Ti-Gravel-Bike-1a.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-Slug-Bikes-Ti-Gravel-Bike-1a.jpg?w=650&amp;quality=75 640w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-Slug-Bikes-Ti-Gravel-Bike-1a.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-Slug-Bikes-Ti-Gravel-Bike-1a.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-Slug-Bikes-Ti-Gravel-Bike-5.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-Slug-Bikes-Ti-Gravel-Bike-5.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-Slug-Bikes-Ti-Gravel-Bike-5.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-Slug-Bikes-Ti-Gravel-Bike-5.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-Slug-Bikes-Ti-Gravel-Bike-2.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-Slug-Bikes-Ti-Gravel-Bike-2.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-Slug-Bikes-Ti-Gravel-Bike-2.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-Slug-Bikes-Ti-Gravel-Bike-2.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-Slug-Bikes-Ti-Gravel-Bike-7.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-Slug-Bikes-Ti-Gravel-Bike-7.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-Slug-Bikes-Ti-Gravel-Bike-7.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-Slug-Bikes-Ti-Gravel-Bike-7.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://slugbicycles.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Slug Bicycles Ti The Earthling Gravel Bike Prototype</a></h3>\n<p>San Francisco-based Slug Bicycles has a new Taiwan-made titanium gravel bike it’s calling The Earthling. It’s the quintessential Bay area dirt bike. The Earthling features a butted Ti tubeset, a seamless asymmetric 3D-printed yoke, UDH, 68mm shell, non-boost, 58mm tire clearance, 75mm bb drop, 435mm stays, 71º head tube and 74º seat tube, with an ENVE Adv fork for now, but a Slug fork is on the way soon-ish. Hell yeah for double water bottle down tube placement!</p>\n<p>Keep your eyes on the <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/slugbicycles/?hl=en\" target=\"_blank\">Slug Instagram</a> for updates!</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-Sage-Droptimator-Drop-Bar-MTB-666.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-Sage-Droptimator-Drop-Bar-MTB-666.jpg?w=650&amp;quality=75 640w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-Sage-Droptimator-Drop-Bar-MTB-666.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-Sage-Droptimator-Drop-Bar-MTB-666.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-Sage-Droptimator-Drop-Bar-MTB-9.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-Sage-Droptimator-Drop-Bar-MTB-9.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-Sage-Droptimator-Drop-Bar-MTB-9.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-Sage-Droptimator-Drop-Bar-MTB-9.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-Sage-Droptimator-Drop-Bar-MTB-14.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-Sage-Droptimator-Drop-Bar-MTB-14.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-Sage-Droptimator-Drop-Bar-MTB-14.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-Sage-Droptimator-Drop-Bar-MTB-14.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-Sage-Droptimator-Drop-Bar-MTB-26.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-Sage-Droptimator-Drop-Bar-MTB-26.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-Sage-Droptimator-Drop-Bar-MTB-26.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-Sage-Droptimator-Drop-Bar-MTB-26.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://sagetitanium.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Sage Droptimator Drop Bar 29er</a></h3>\n<p>The all-new Sage Titanium Droptimator is a cross between the brand’s hardtail and gravel race bikes. Dubbed the Droptimator, it’s designed around a 69º head angle, splitting the difference between the Optimator hardtail’s slack 67.5º head angle and Storm King gravel bike’s 70.5º head angle. Its geometry is nestled between gravel and hardtail to create a purpose-built <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/drop-bar-29er-mountain-bikes/\" target=\"_blank\">drop bar 29er</a> that’s capable on mixed terrain rides. Sage shortened the top tube on the Droptimator and head tube to give it appropriate reach and stack figures, then paired it with a 100 mm travel SID XC suspension fork, a bit shorter than the Optimator’s 120 mm travel.</p>\n<p>Check out more at <a href=\"https://sagetitanium.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Sage</a>!</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-Bens-Mosaic-Small-Monsters-Livery-3.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-Bens-Mosaic-Small-Monsters-Livery-3.jpg?w=650&amp;quality=75 640w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-Bens-Mosaic-Small-Monsters-Livery-3.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-Bens-Mosaic-Small-Monsters-Livery-3.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-Bens-Mosaic-Small-Monsters-Livery-15.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-Bens-Mosaic-Small-Monsters-Livery-15.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-Bens-Mosaic-Small-Monsters-Livery-15.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-Bens-Mosaic-Small-Monsters-Livery-15.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-Bens-Mosaic-Small-Monsters-Livery-9.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-Bens-Mosaic-Small-Monsters-Livery-9.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-Bens-Mosaic-Small-Monsters-Livery-9.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-Bens-Mosaic-Small-Monsters-Livery-9.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-Bens-Mosaic-Small-Monsters-Livery-68.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-Bens-Mosaic-Small-Monsters-Livery-68.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-Bens-Mosaic-Small-Monsters-Livery-68.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-Bens-Mosaic-Small-Monsters-Livery-68.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.thesmallmonstersproject.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Ben Frederick’s The Small Monsters Project Custom Mosaic GT-1 45 ‘Cross</a></h3>\n<p>Ben Frederick and the Small Monsters Project are here racing bikes, sharing stoke, and enjoying his “local” event. After a successful European Cyclocross campaign this past winter, he’s racing his custom <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/tag/mosaic-cycles/\" target=\"_blank\">Mosaic</a> GT-1 45 gravel bike at the Lifetime Series gravel race (also known as Long Form Cyclocross – lol). The rest of the week, you can catch him doing his day job at the Ornot Booth. Ben was a music major. Swing by the <a href=\"https://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;merchant_id=34a711d0-83d2-4a96-8e01-9f5ea4abd1fc&amp;website_id=6ec3743b-a948-4c16-9d12-4b79ac107f25&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ornotbike.com%2F\" target=\"_blank\">Ornot</a> booth and try to guess what instrument he played.</p>\n<p>Thanks to Ben for always being a good sport with these fun photos! Check out more at <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/benjamfred/?hl=en\" target=\"_blank\">Ben’s Instagram</a>!</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/1-Up_Mojave_2025-5.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/1-Up_Mojave_2025-5.jpg?w=650&amp;quality=75 640w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/1-Up_Mojave_2025-5.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/1-Up_Mojave_2025-5.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p><em>John en route to Sea Otter in the Mojave Desert. Please respect our public lands and observe the <a href=\"https://lnt.org/\" target=\"_blank\">Leave No Trace</a> and <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/from-biocrust-with-love/\" target=\"_blank\">Shred Lightly Principles</a>! </em></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><strong>The Radavist thanks <a href=\"https://1up-usa.com/\" target=\"_blank\">1-Up USA</a> for sponsoring our Sea Otter Classic coverage and our independent Reportage!</strong></p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/2025-sea-otter-marin-hudski-mondraker-slug-sage-mosaic/\">2025 Sea Otter Classic Prelude: PNW Marin Giveaway Bike, Hudski Dualist Hardtail, Mondraker Grinduro Edition, Slug Ti Gravel Bike, Sage Dropimator, and Small Monsters Mosaic</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://theradavist.com\">The Radavist</a>.</p>","author":"John Watson","siteTitle":"The Radavist","siteHash":"96eb481d8084f04a4602bac57874ba717baf56b758f45547b5caf2312da766ef","entryHash":"3329e87d111bf61c4b7afbfefeecd6bc6114cafb9a67c0a85f9c81c5c2ea5049","category":"Cycling"}